{"tid":592036,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"理大研究　輕步跑減六成受傷風險","createTime":"2018-03-14T02:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T03:13:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"35a27d3750dcecfe6073b70a45cdca25b4884dce","tid":592036,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:26:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180314/20331483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F20331483&d=xxv2JTlsdH3wx2T%2F0G90%2FAIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=be2b3e96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F20331483&h=b6f2994a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180314/20331483</a><br />\n<br />\n理大研究　輕步跑減六成受傷風險<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180314/large/0313long2005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180314%2Flarge%2F0313long2005.jpg&h=e9de6748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n理大研究發現跑步輕着地可減受傷風險。夏家朗攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】理大研究發現，九成跑手會先以腳踭落地。專家建議跑手以腳部中掌着地，輕着地去跑，可減少受傷風險達62%。<br />\n<br />\n理大於2016年開展「步姿訓練計劃」，招募320名18至50歲、跑齡不足兩年的長跑初學者，並分設步姿訓練組和對照組。他們會先接受兩周共8次的跑步訓練，其中步姿訓練組的166人在跑步機跑步期間會提醒他們「跑輕一點」，另外154人對照組則不作提醒。<br />\n<br />\n他們之後每周平均跑約7公里，理大收集各人長達1年的數據，包括跑步里數、訓練和受傷報告。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全掌着地降低撞擊力<br />\n<br />\n理大統計過相關數據，對照組跑者共報告61宗受傷案例，佔該組的38%；輕步跑者只報告28宗受傷個案，僅佔該組的16%。由此計算，步姿訓練可將受傷機會降低了62%。至於受傷個案中，對照組有23宗足底筋膜炎和18宗膝關節疼痛報告，輕步跑者分別只有兩宗和4宗。步姿訓練組則只有10宗小腿跟腱炎和小腿拉傷個案。<br />\n<br />\n理大康復治療科學系副教授張子熙解釋，部份步姿訓練組跑者或使用前掌着地，反令腳踝蹠屈受壓，令小腿受傷，但受傷比率仍較對照組低。<br />\n<br />\n張子熙表示，有九成跑手都會先以腳踭落地，引致過度勞損、髕股關節痛、足底筋膜炎或髂脛束綜合症等問題。他建議市民跑姿可改以全掌着地，降低着地的撞擊力，而跑姿改變一般約兩星期即可適應。<br />\n<br />\n張又稱，縮短步幅或增加步頻，例如由一分鐘120至130步，增至約160至180步，以及身體稍向前傾，也可減少受傷風險。<br />\n<br />\n■記者羅繼盛"},{"pid":"68da01523dd4cfebff09925d2968a3bd0b5f9100","tid":592036,"uid":101895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:31:32.000Z","msg":"直接買對Air 跑啦傻鳩"},{"pid":"4f7a8a8aa2d6afacd3f9b7853c184b92dc97f8a9","tid":592036,"uid":66610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"即係pose running ?"},{"pid":"4e3e363982b8ab67db0d343b3b5e54b9340e78fc","tid":592036,"uid":38143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:33:33.000Z","msg":"陸王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd352f4fbac2a45d6ed265d7cd2665b760fa6aa","tid":592036,"uid":45591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e3e363982b8ab67db0d343b3b5e54b9340e78fc","tid":592036,"uid":38143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:33:33.000Z","msg":"陸王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:34:50.000Z","msg":"我都諗起陸王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e252af7f9894f1c08cfc6e8e01209b889ca9fe7","tid":592036,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:36:02.000Z","msg":"我通常凌空跑"},{"pid":"f5127aacebab81c6b4507ed5baefdbe762ecbca3","tid":592036,"uid":6530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:38:51.000Z","msg":"雙腳唔掂地唔會受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713165effb3bf5e0e3ef18e5829ee769899de23a","tid":592036,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dd352f4fbac2a45d6ed265d7cd2665b760fa6aa","tid":592036,"uid":45591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e3e363982b8ab67db0d343b3b5e54b9340e78fc","tid":592036,"uid":38143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T02:33:33.000Z","msg":"陸王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-